OL,3,CFootball fan jailed after shouting
OL,4,C'horrific and violent' racial slurs at
OL,5,Cplayer
OL,7,FA football fan has been sentenced to
OL,8,Fnine months in prison and banned from
OL,9,Fmatches for six years after admitting
OL,10,Fracially abusing a Forest Green Rovers
OL,11,Ffootball player.
OL,13,FRyan Ferguson, 24 and from Liverpool,
OL,14,Fshouted what's been described as
OL,15,F'horrific and violent' abuse at
OL,16,Fforward Jordon Garrick at the New Lawn
OL,17,Fin April 2023.
OL,19,FHe's one of the first people in the
OL,20,Fcountry to be jailed for such an
OL,21,Foffence.
