OL,3,CFootball fan jailed after shouting
OL,4,C'horrific and violent' racial slurs at
OL,5,Cplayer
OL,7,FThis followed a previous guilty plea
OL,8,Fto racially aggravated public order,
OL,9,Fbeing a football spectator failing to
OL,10,Fcomply with a football banning order
OL,11,Funder the Football Spectators Act 1989
OL,12,Fand obstructing a constable in the
OL,13,Fexecution of their duty.
OL,15,FGarrick said he was shaken by the
OL,16,Fincident and the language used were
OL,17,F'words no one should have to hear'.
