OL,3,CFootball fan jailed after shouting
OL,4,C'horrific and violent' racial slurs at
OL,5,Cplayer
OL,7,FThe court heard how Ferguson, a
OL,8,FTranmere Rovers fan who was subject to
OL,9,Fa five year football banning order,
OL,10,Fattended the New Lawn after receiving
OL,11,Fa complimentary ticket.
OL,13,FAround 35 minutes into the first half
OL,14,Fof the game, Forest Green Rovers were
OL,15,Fawarded a throw in by the West Stand
OL,16,Fcorner of the pitch.
OL,18,FAt the time a Forest Green Rovers
OL,19,Fplayer was tussling with a Fleetwood
OL,20,FTown defender.
