OL,3,CFootball fan jailed after shouting
OL,4,C'horrific and violent' racial slurs at
OL,5,Cplayer
OL,7,FThe referee came over to speak to the
OL,8,Fplayers and there was a moment of
OL,9,Fsilence. In this moment Ferguson
OL,10,Fshouted racial abuse Jordon Garrick.
OL,12,FThis was heard by a number of players
OL,13,Fon the pitch who reacted to Ferguson's
OL,14,Fabuse. It was also heard by club
OL,15,Fsecurity personnel and others in the
OL,16,Fstand.
OL,18,FThe whole incident was captured on
OL,19,FCCTV and minutes later he was escorted
OL,20,Fout of the stands by security.
