OL,7,FHe was then questioned by police where
OL,8,Fhe gave false details before being
OL,9,Farrested. It later emerged he already
OL,10,Fhad five-year football banning order,
OL,11,Fimposed in 2019.
OL,13,FIn a written victim impact statement,
OL,14,FJordon Garrick said: "Forest Green
OL,15,FRovers Football Club and the Bolt New
OL,16,FLawn Stadium is my place of work, when
OL,17,FI am on the pitch as a player, I am at
OL,18,Fwork.
