OL,3,CFootball fan jailed after shouting
OL,4,C'horrific and violent' racial slurs at
OL,5,Cplayer
OL,7,F"I understand there will always be a
OL,8,Fcrowd in the stands watching me and my
OL,9,Fteammates play.
OL,11,F"I am aware that fans will vocally
OL,12,Fexpress their enjoyment or
OL,13,Fdisappointment at a football match,
OL,14,Fbut I should never have to be
OL,15,Fsubjected to racially offensive verbal
OL,16,Fabuse while at work.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G6/12
