OL,3,CFootball fan jailed after shouting
OL,4,C'horrific and violent' racial slurs at
OL,5,Cplayer
OL,7,F"I find this type of abuse grossly
OL,8,Foffensive. I was shocked at the
OL,9,Fdisgusting language used against me,
OL,10,Fthese are words that no-one should
OL,11,Fever hear."
OL,13,FFollowing sentencing PC Adrian Tuft, a
OL,14,Fdedicated football officer at
OL,15,FGloucestershire Constabulary said:
OL,16,F"Ferguson is a persistent football
OL,17,Foffender, this is not the first time
OL,18,Fthat he has breached his banning order.
