OL,3,CFootball fan jailed after shouting
OL,4,C'horrific and violent' racial slurs at
OL,5,Cplayer
OL,7,F"On this occasion Ferguson breached
OL,8,Fhis order using horrendous racial
OL,9,Fabuse which was clearly heard by the
OL,10,Fintended victim and a number of his
OL,11,Fteammates.
OL,13,F"Clearly Ferguson cannot be trusted
OL,14,Finside a football ground or its
OL,15,Fimmediate vicinity on a match day. We
OL,16,Fwould encourage all football
OL,17,Fsupporters to report any racial,
OL,18,Fhomophobic or other hateful abuse to
OL,19,Fthe club, to The FA, Kick It Out, or
OL,20,Fthe police.
