OL,3,CFootball fan jailed after shouting
OL,4,C'horrific and violent' racial slurs at
OL,5,Cplayer
OL,7,F"As a Force we treat these reports
OL,8,Fwith the utmost seriousness and will
OL,9,Fwork closely with the clubs, the FA
OL,10,Fand the UK Football Policing Unit to
OL,11,Fidentify any suspects and prosecute
OL,12,Fthem to the full extent of the law."
OL,14,FChief Constable Mark Roberts, NPCC
OL,15,Flead for Football Policing, said:
OL,16,F"Racist abuse will not be tolerated in
OL,17,Ffootball stadiums, and I'm pleased the
OL,18,Fcourt has recognised the seriousness
OL,19,Fof these offences and issued a prison
OL,20,Fsentence in this case.
