OL,3,CFootball fan jailed after shouting
OL,4,C'horrific and violent' racial slurs at
OL,5,Cplayer
OL,7,F"We can see from Jordon Garrick's
OL,8,Fstatement the impact this abuse has
OL,9,Fhad on him. No-one should ever have to
OL,10,Fexperience this, not least at their
OL,11,Fplace of work.
OL,13,F"Breaching a football banning order is
OL,14,Falso a serious offence, and I'm
OL,15,Fpleased to see that a further six-year
OL,16,Forder has been issued in this case.
