OL,5,Cplayer
OL,7,F"We collectively need to make football
OL,8,Fa safe environment for the
OL,9,Foverwhelming majority of fans want to
OL,10,Fenjoy the game, and anyone who commits
OL,11,Fa criminal offence either outside or
OL,12,Finside a football ground can expect to
OL,13,Fface the consequences of their
OL,14,Factions."
OL,16,FA spokesperson for Forest Green Rovers
OL,17,Fadded: "Forest Green Rovers FC, along
OL,18,Fwith every other football club,
OL,19,Fdeplore the use of racist abuse and
OL,20,Flanguage which has no place in our
OL,21,Fgame or our society.
