OL,5,Cplayer
OL,7,F"Nobody should be subjected to the
OL,8,Fracist abuse that our player Jordon
OL,9,FGarrick was back in April and we
OL,10,Fwelcome the sentencing administered by
OL,11,Fthe court.
OL,13,F"We sincerely hope that this sends a
OL,14,Fstrong message to the individual
OL,15,Finvolved in this case and those
OL,16,Fpersons that share a similar view that
OL,17,Fthis behaviour is unacceptable and
OL,18,Fwill not be tolerated."
